query:
INSERT INTO inventory_transactions (inventoryId, skuId, transactionType, quantityKg, notes, createdAt) 
SELECT i.id, i.skuId, 'purchase', ROUND(10 + RAND() * 20, 2), 'Initial stock from Marukyu Koyamaen', DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 30 DAY)
FROM inventory i
UNION ALL
SELECT i.id, i.skuId, 'purchase', ROUND(5 + RAND() * 15, 2), 'Restock shipment', DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 14 DAY)
FROM inventory i
UNION ALL
SELECT i.id, i.skuId, 'allocation', ROUND(2 + RAND() * 5, 2), 'Allocated to client order', DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 7 DAY)
FROM inventory i;
